reviewText: This season is a bit darker and even has a few characters dying. Really good production value. There are still bright and happy episodes in between the darker ones.

I am a huge 'Angry Birds' fan. This DVD has the same craziness as the complete first season DVD.
This DVD is awesome!
My son LOVES this! He is an Angry Bird fanatic, and Stella is his favorite, so he was very happy when I got this for him
My kids loved Season 1, however Season 2 scared them several times, and we stopped watching it.  I would not recommend this for young kids.
